S4PA/Receiving Version $Revision: 1.1.1.1 $ (S4PA $Name:  $)
===============================================

This module contains methods for data transfer, metadata extraction, metadata
conversion to XML and disk allocation.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

S4P
S4P::PDR
S4P::PAN
S4P::FileGroup
S4P::FileSpec
S4P::TimeTools
Net::SSH2
Net::SSH2::SFTP
Net::SSH2::File
Net::FTP
Net::Netrc
File::Basename
File::KGlob
File::stat
XML::LibXML
Fcntl

